comm_text: Samuel Taylor (Tranmere Rovers) wins a free kick on the right wing.
Foul by Jake Batty (Accrington Stanley).
Attempt blocked. Lee O'Connor (Tranmere Rovers) right footed shot from outside the box is blocked. Assisted by Regan Hendry.
Corner, Tranmere Rovers. Conceded by Ben Woods.
Corner, Tranmere Rovers. Conceded by Liam Coyle.
Attempt missed. Tom Davies (Tranmere Rovers) header from the centre of the box is close, but misses to the left. Assisted by Kieron Morris with a cross following a corner.
Corner, Tranmere Rovers. Conceded by Jake Batty.
Fourth official has announced 11 minutes of added time.
